00:45:14.300 --> 00:45:16.459
aggressive nationalism,
tied to imperialism and

00:45:16.459 --> 00:45:18.289
economic rivalry and everything
else,

00:45:18.289 --> 00:45:21.550
helps explain how this war came
about.

00:45:21.550 --> 00:45:24.872
And the idea of how people
